,{"pid":"b96a5e7ffc87ad0b4729a4b200a3832085223520","tid":468073,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T11:39:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人生80年有80個挫折有幾奇?<br />\n有成功就有失敗 <br />\n街上每個人都背負住各種既挫折<br />\n<br />\n當你呢刻達唔成預期結果時<br />\n應該就翻現有結果<br />\n去諗下未來點樣再達到你既目標</blockquote><br />\n無數個小挫折<br />\n<br />\n加上呢個大挫折<br />\n<br />\n唔識點樣企返起身<br />\n<br />\n如果而家係捉緊棋<br />\n<br />\n我好想cum旗投降"},{"pid":"c1f2c62bb289044779fcd3148b426bd6170f2ad4","tid":468073,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T11:39:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平係平<br />\n<br />\n出乎意料地唔難飲</blockquote><br />\n唔好飲太多 傷身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飲水咁<br />\n<br />\n殊一聲飲晒<br />\n<br />\n人生都係咁順利就好囉"},{"pid":"8194db838c8841facdc0e78b703298744f147296","tid":468073,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T11:40:34.000Z","msg":"想訓個長覺<br />\n<br />\n乜都唔想理"},{"pid":"dc8fa05336fa1c27742e7c167ef12336e77d890e","tid":468073,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T11:41:16.000Z","msg":"步伐沉重<br />\n<br />\n但好似行屍走肉咁行唔停"},{"pid":"45f28233fa619cdf6fad1237cf98d97d89ce1189","tid":468073,"uid":40337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T11:43:41.000Z","msg":"唔開心 我通常都會去圖書館<br />\n你可以試下"},{"pid":"2793f955d7c2f4d84077b265a85d31cf0927f101","tid":468073,"uid":139264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T11:45:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>平係平<br />\n<br />\n出乎意料地唔難飲</blockquote><br />\n唔好飲太多 傷身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飲水咁<br />\n<br />\n殊一聲飲晒<br />\n<br />\n人生都係咁順利就好囉</blockquote><br />\n暢快喊一次 再重新起步"},{"pid":"c74df9c374b8394dfc33f774b053e0efa7b47b34","tid":468073,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T11:46:43.000Z","msg":"小挫折無限放大<br />\n小成功拋諸腦